ingredients: SUGAR, CORN SYRUP, WATER, ENRICHED BLEACHED FLOUR (WHEAT FLOUR, BARLEY MALT, NIACIN, REDUCED IRON, THIAMIN MONONITRATE [VITAMIN B1], RIBOFLAVIN [VITAMIN B2], FOLIC ACID), PALM AND PALM KERNEL OIL, PALM AND SOYBEAN OILS WITH TBHQ AND CITRIC ACID TO PROTECT FLAVOR, COCOA, SOYBEAN OIL. CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF EACH OF THE FOLLOWING: SOY FLOUR, COCOA PROCESSED WITH ALKALI, DEXTROSE, CORN STARCH, EGG WHITES, EGGS, COLORS (CARAMEL COLOR, RED 40), SALT, BAKING SODA, SORBIC ACID (TO PRESERVE FRESHNESS), MONO-AND DIGLYCERIDES, SOY LECITHIN, SORBITAN MONOSTEARATE, SOYBEAN OIL, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVORS, PROPYLENE GLYCOL MONOSTEARATE, SODIUM STEAROYL LACTYLATE, POLYSORBATE 60, POLYSORBATE 80, WHEY (MILK), CITRIC ACID.
